axb6 (13... Bg4 $5 $17) 14. Qe2 Nxc4 15. Qxc4 c6 16. dxc6 bxc6 17. Nd4 Ba6 $17)
({Similar to the previous note is} 10. Ndb5 d5 11. exd5 Ne5 12. Bxb6 axb6 $1
$146 {Black should not give up the possibility of undermining white's d-pawn
by means of ...c7-c6} (12... cxb6 $6 13. d6 N7g6 14. f4 $16 {1-0 (27) Vukovic,
